==UCI teams==
{{main|List of 2017 UCI Women's Teams and riders}}
The country designation of each team is determined by the country of registration of the largest number of its riders, and is not necessarily the country where the team is registered or based.<ref>{{cite book|title=UCI Cycling Regulations, Part 2: Road Races |publisher=[[Union Cycliste Internationale|UCI]] |at=Clause 2.17.006, page 160 |url=http://www.uci.ch/includes/asp/getTarget.asp?type=FILE&id=34028 |date=1 July 2012 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110623174023/http://www.uci.ch/Modules/BUILTIN/getObject.asp?MenuId=MTkzNg&ObjTypeCode=FILE&type=FILE&id=34028&LangId=1 |archivedate=23 June 2011 }}</ref>

