'''[[China]]''' was participate in the [[2012 Asian Beach Games]] in [[Haiyang]], [[China]] on 16–22 June 2012.

China also won 14 gold medals, 10 silver medals, 12 bronze medals and a total of 39 medals, finishing first on the medal table.<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.ocasia.org/NOCs/NocCountries.aspx?ap3QYtg6k0A= |title=PARTICIPATING AT THE ASIAN GAMES AND MEDALS}}</ref>

