{{Infobox Minor League Baseball |name = Dominican Summer League Reds |founded = |city = Boca Chica |misc = |logo = NLC-CIN-Logo.png |uniformlogo = Cincinnati Reds Cap Insignia.svg |class level = Rookie |past class level= |current league = [[Dominican Summer League]] |conference = |division = Boca Chica Baseball City |past league = |majorleague = [[Cincinnati Reds]] |pastmajorleague = |nickname = Reds |pastnames = |ballpark = Baseball City Complex |pastparks = |leaguenum = 0 |leaguechamps = None |divnum = 0 |divisionchamps = |owner = Cincinnati Reds |manager = Luis Saturria |gm = }}
The '''Dominican Summer League Reds''' are a minor league baseball team of the [[Dominican Summer League]]. They are located in Boca Chica, Santo Domingo, Dominican Republic, and play their home games at Ciudad de Baseball. The team plays in the Boca Chica Baseball City division and is affiliated with the [[Cincinnati Reds]].
