'''Sayed Mohammad Ayub''' (born 20 November 1908, date of death unknown) was an [[Afghanistan]] field hockey player, who competed at the [[1936 Summer Olympic Games]] and played in both games.<ref>[https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/ay/sayed-mohammad-ayub-1.html Sports-Reference Profile]</ref>

