{{Infobox football biography | name = Tawfiq Ali | image = | fullname = Tawfiq Ali Abu Hammad | height = {{height|m=1.97}} | birth_date = {{birth date and age|1990|11|8|df=y}} | birth_place = [[Gaza City|Gaza]], [[State of Palestine|Palestine]] | currentclub = [[Shabab Al-Khalil SC|Shabab Al-Khalil]] | clubnumber = 1 | position = [[Goalkeeper (association football)|Goalkeeper]] | youthyears1 = | youthclubs1 = [[Tarji Wadi Al-Nes]] | years1 = 2011–2015 | years2 = 2015–2016 | years3 = 2016– | clubs1 = [[Tarji Wadi Al-Nes]] | clubs2 = [[Shabab Dura]] | clubs3 = [[Shabab Al-Khalil SC|Shabab Al-Khalil]] | caps1 = 36 | caps2 = | caps3 = | goals1 = 0 | goals2 = | goals3 = | nationalyears1 = 2009–2012 | nationalyears2 = 2011– | nationalteam1 = [[Palestine national football team|Palestine U23]] | nationalteam2 = [[Palestine national football team|Palestine]] | nationalcaps1 = 10 | nationalgoals1 = 0 | nationalcaps2 = 27 | nationalgoals2 = 0 | club-update = 6 June 2014 | nationalteam-update = 9 November 2015 }}
'''Tawfiq Ali Abuhammad''' ({{lang-ar|توفيق علي}}; born 8 November 1990) is a [[State of Palestine|Palestinian]] [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Goalkeeper (association football)|goalkeeper]] for the [[Palestine national football team]] and [[Tarji Wadi Al-Nes]] in the [[West Bank Premier League]].<ref>{{cite web|title=توفيق علي أبو حماد|url=http://www.kooora.com/?player=55494|language=Arabic|publisher=كووورة|accessdate=13 February 2015}}</ref>
He received his first senior cap in the bronze medal match of the [[Football at the 2011 Pan Arab Games|2011 Pan Arab Games]] against [[Kuwait national football team|Kuwait]]. His first clean sheet as national team goalkeeper came on 29 February 2012 in a friendly against [[Azerbaijan national football team|Azerbaijan]], that ended with a 2–0 win for Palestine.<ref>{{cite web|title=Palestine 2 - 0 Azerbaijan|url=https://uk.eurosport.yahoo.com/football/international-friendlies/2012/palestine-azerbaijan-502635.html|publisher=Yahoo Eurosport UK|date=29 February 2012|accessdate=13 February 2015}}</ref>
