The '''Tour des Pays de Savoie''' is a [[stage race|staged]] cycling race held annually in the departments of [[Savoie]] and [[Haute-Savoie]] in [[France]]. It was created in 1999 and is part of the [[UCI Europe Tour]] in category [[2.2]].

